title: Cyclist arrested in scuffle with DBKL over impounded bikes
text:
A 23-year old cyclist was this morning arrested over an alleged scuffle with Kuala Lumpur City Hall (DBKL) officers during a protest against the local authorityâ€™s move to impound parked bicycles. 
Sukri Kaman told Malaysiakini the cyclist will be arrested tomorrow. 
He said a police report was lodged by a DBKL officer who was allegedly assaulted by the cyclist at about 10.15am.
